  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never forget-- for my job I [? had ?] received 50 groszy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was rather nice salary-- not salary-- nice tip.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, besides this tip, I received wonderful bouillon with chicken.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was so delicious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, when I said my mother that I ate in this Jew restaurant, and she said, yes, the-- the bouillon is excellent because it is kosher poultry, and there is never dirty [INAUDIBLE] in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And therefore the taste [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in this restaurant they served only a half chicken with some pasta-- with some noodles, or macaroni as you say-- some-- nothing more.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I never forget when I make the shopping [? dinner, ?] I was so keen not for this 50 groszy, but only for this bouillon soup.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not so very big.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's say maybe 60,000 of inhabitants, but we [? haved ?] our own theatre.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had wonderful [? four ?] old church.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was like-- we called it, like Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Torun was more Venezia [? in ?] Norden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Thanks God Torun during the war wasn't-- not destroyed, not ruined-- so that everything original is until now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even the house where was born the very famous [? astronaus, ?] Mikolaj Kopernik-- or the German people and all over they say Nicolaus Copernicus in Latin.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we say Mikolaj Kopernik.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were also, but I never went to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, I was a child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was working by German gardener.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- maybe he is not alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can mention his name now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Bartel. ?] I never forget this name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Very good guy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He paid me also with some Polish coins.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But usually I received in a bag plenty of vegetables so that I could take this to my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
